Mushroom Pizza

35 min
$12.99
800 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

dairygluten

Dietary Tags:

vegetarianhigh-protein

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

quick mealeasy dinnerpizza

Description

A delightful and savory pizza topped with a medley of mushrooms and melted cheese, perfect for a quick meal.

Ingredients

  • pre-made pizza crust: 1
  • pizza sauce: 1/2 cup
  • mozzarella cheese: 1 1/2 cups
  • mixed mushrooms (e.g., button, cremini, shiitake): 2 cups
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • fresh basil: 1/4 cup
  • parmesan cheese: 1/4 cup
